'''Pat Nebo''', ni umuhanzi [[Nijeriya|wo]] muri Nigeriya wapanze umusaruro nkumuyobozi wubuhanzi<ref>https://www.premiumtimesng.com/entertainment/nollywood/377525-interview-my-career-as-nollywood-production-designer-pat-nebo.html</ref> .   Yakoze nk'umushinga wo gutunganya amashusho muri firime harimo''October 1'', ''"76'', ''Being Mrs Elliot'' and ''Okafor's Law'' .    Yakoze kandi nkuwashushanyije muri firime nke.<ref>https://www.thisdaylive.com/index.php/2021/09/19/pat-nebo-tunde-kelani-deserves-a-national-honour/</ref> 

Mu 1993, yatangiye umwuga we wo gutunganya ibicuruzwa hamwe na firime yo murugo ''Ti oluwa ni ile''<ref>https://mubi.com/cast/pat-nebo</ref> . Muri uwo mwaka, yakoze mu bice bibiri bya ''Ti oluwa ni ile'' . Mu mwaka wa 2009, yagaragaye muri sinema ya mbere muri filime yitwa ''Figurine'' aho yakinnye nka 'Umubitsi w'ishyingirwa'<ref>http://worldcat.org/identities/np-nebo,%20pat</ref>. Icyakora, yakomeje gukora ''nkuwashushanyije'' muri firime nyinshi nka Araromire, ''Arugba'', ''Symphony ya Alero'' na ''Kuba Madamu Elliot''<ref>https://nollysilverscreen.com/2021/09/10/attend-the-filmmakers-forum-with-pat-nebo/</ref> . Usibye gushushanya umusaruro, yanakoze nk'umuyobozi wubuhanzi muri firime: ''The Figurine'', ''Terefone Swap'', ''IHalf of a Yellow Sun'' na ''76''<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1428032-pat-nebo</ref> .

